  "generated_text": "To find the total number of bolts of fiber required for the robe, we need to determine the amount of blue and white fiber separately and then add them together.\n\n1.  **Calculate the amount of blue fiber:**\n    The problem states that the robe takes 2 bolts of blue fiber.\n    $$ \\text{Blue bolts} = 2 $$\n\n2.  **Calculate the amount of white fiber:**\n    The problem states that the white fiber is \"half that much\" (half of the blue amount).\n    $$ \\text{White bolts} = \\frac{1}{2} \\times 2 = 1 $$\n\n3.  **Calculate the total number of bolts:**\n    Add the blue and white bolts together.\n    $$ \\text{Total bolts} = \\text{Blue bolts} + \\text{White bolts} $$\n    $$ \\text{Total bolts} = 2 + 1 = 3 $$\n\n\\boxed{3}\n",
